description:
Added a Drop A# guitar for people who have a lower tuned normal guitar.
For reference, you need a baritone guitar to be at standard A# and other lower standard tunings. Drop A and Drop A# can be achieved with thicker strings and remember to set your bridge correctly if you have a Floyd rose.
title: Somewhere I Belong

description: Fixed guitars, tuning and slight edits to bass.
